# SmartThings Motion Sensor Enhanced for Hubitat

**Author:** Jdthomas24
**Namespace:** jdthomas24
**Version:** 1.0

## Description

Custom Hubitat driver for SmartThings Zigbee motion sensors. Provides reliable local motion detection, battery reporting, and seamless integration with Hubitat automation apps.

## Installation

Install via Hubitat Package Manager or manual driver import.

Pair device using Zigbee discovery in Hubitat.

Assign the SmartThings Motion driver if not automatically selected.

Use in Rule Machine, Motion Lighting, or Dashboards for automation.

## Notes

Device may initially pair as a generic device — manually assign the driver if needed.

Battery updates depend on device reporting intervals and may not update instantly.

Zigbee mesh quality can impact motion responsiveness and reporting reliability.
